# **3.0 Expected Table Structure**

## **Project Table**

| Field               | Type    |
| ------------------- | ------- |
| project_id          | int     |
| client_name         | varchar |
| location            | varchar |
| manager_name        | varchar |
| project_description | varchar |
| project_name        | varchar |
| duration            | int     |

---

## **Bug Table**

| Field           | Type     |
| --------------- | -------- |
| bug_id          | int      |
| bug_description | varchar  |
| bug_type        | varchar  |
| severity        | int      |
| status          | varchar  |
| project_id      | int (FK) |

👉 `project_id` is the **join column**

